{"type": "article", "id": 8312, "title": "Dream Tools 梦幻桌面", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-10T07:19:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234722d7emOn6c5AW9a8NF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这款产品同样来自 Lexon，但是另外一个设计师 Eugeni Quitllet 的作品，这款叫做 Dream Tools 的桌面用品组合和它的名字一样如梦似幻，包括 Peter Pen 钢笔以及笔筒，Roll Air 胶带卷盘，Liquid Station 流动型桌面摆台，可以智能手机、钢笔和名片等，还有一个叫做 Dream Time 的闹钟。这些产品既是组合产品又各自独立，允许单独购买，价格在 15 到 50 欧元之间。<a href=\"http://www.lexon-design.com/capsules/dream-tools.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234720vPiX7RG8QLeB6V2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.503125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234720w0vGWAcIp9N76jzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234720HnCIN6fDdV5etQw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234721dR89LlsOrhvPmV5C.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234721oTXh6dKiFDLRnAVz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}